data.description: Move-in ready; meticulously cared for & maintained.  Two story brick home with great curb appeal is ready for you!  Home features 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, open floor plan, two eating areas, LARGE bedrooms and a wood burning stone fireplace in the living room.  Flowing floor plan, versatile living/dining areas, & sizable back yard with covered porch & extended patio provide perfect places for entertainment.  HUGE master suite w/updated bath & custom walk-in closet, along with garden tub & separate shower.  Roof approx 3-4 yrs old & HVAC approx 6 yrs old.  You will be located close to RAFB, Ft Sam, I35 & shopping.  Come make this house your home.  Easy to show.
